    user_response: "You are a world-class senior frontend engineer, luxury UI engineer, motion designer, and product designer.\n\n\n\nYour task:\n\n\n\nDesign and implement ONLY the FRONTEND of an elite premium portfolio website for Adarsh Singh.\n\n\n\nDO NOT build backend yet.\n\n\n\nHowever:\n\n\n\nThe architecture MUST be clean, modular, scalable, and READY to connect with a Python backend later (FastAPI/Django/Flask compatible).\n\n\n\nEverything must be componentized and production-grade.\n\n\n\nThe final portfolio must feel:\n\n\n\nApple keynote \303\227 Luxury tech founder website \303\227 Premium futuristic interface.\n\n\n\nNOT a normal developer portfolio.\n\n\n\nThe website must instantly communicate:\n\n\n\nLuxury > Elite > Trustworthy > Futuristic > Creative > Powerful\n\n\n\nThe website should feel:\n\n\n\n\342\200\234This person is elite.\342\200\235\n\n\n\nwhile still being recruiter-friendly and easy to scan in 30 seconds.\n\n\n\n---------------------------------------------------\n\nTECH STACK (MANDATORY)\n\n---------------------------------------------------\n\n\n\nFrontend Only:\n\n\n\n- Next.js 15 (App Router)\n\n- TypeScript\n\n- TailwindCSS\n\n- Framer Motion\n\n- shadcn/ui\n\n- Lucide React Icons\n\n- next-themes\n\n- clsx\n\n- tailwind-merge\n\n\n\nOptional for hero animation only:\n\n- GSAP (minimal use)\n\n\n\nNO backend implementation.\n\n\n\nBut architecture MUST be backend-ready.\n\n\n\nPrepare API abstraction layer:\n\n\n\n/services\n\n/api\n\n/hooks\n\n/types\n\n\n\nfor future Python backend integration.\n\n\n\nUse mock JSON data for now.\n\n\n\n---------------------------------------------------\n\nDESIGN PHILOSOPHY\n\n---------------------------------------------------\n\n\n\nThe UI should feel like:\n\n\n\n50% Apple luxury\n\n30% tech founder personal brand\n\n20% futuristic premium\n\n\n\nDO NOT make:\n\n\n\n\342\235\214 template portfolio\n\n\342\235\214 GitHub card portfolio\n\n\342\235\214 dashboard-looking UI\n\n\342\235\214 cyberpunk neon\n\n\342\235\214 over-animated developer clich\303\251\n\n\342\235\214 flashy particles everywhere\n\n\n\nDO create:\n\n\n\n\342\234\205 premium spacing\n\n\342\234\205 Apple-level typography\n\n\342\234\205 luxury hierarchy\n\n\342\234\205 recruiter readability\n\n\342\234\205 subtle futuristic richness\n\n\342\234\205 cinematic motion\n\n\342\234\205 premium glass morphism (minimal)\n\n\342\234\205 dark/light luxury compatibility\n\n\342\234\205 WOW factor\n\n\n\nEverything should feel expensive.\n\n\n\n---------------------------------------------------\n\nTHEME SYSTEM\n\n---------------------------------------------------\n\n\n\nFULL DARK + LIGHT MODE SUPPORT\n\n\n\nAUTO-DETECT SYSTEM PREFERENCE.\n\n\n\nAlso manual toggle.\n\n\n\nLIGHT MODE:\n\nTitanium luxury aesthetic.\n\n\n\nFeel:\n\nApple website\n\nclean\n\nsoft shadows\n\nsilver gradients\n\npremium whites\n\n\n\nDARK MODE:\n\nObsidian elite luxury.\n\n\n\nColors:\n\nBackground: #050505\n\nGraphite cards\n\nSubtle deep electric blue glow\n\nVery premium contrast\n\n\n\nNo harsh colors.\n\n\n\nNo neon.\n\n\n\nNo bright gradients.\n\n\n\nLuxury only.\n\n\n\n---------------------------------------------------\n\nTYPOGRAPHY\n\n---------------------------------------------------\n\n\n\nTypography matters heavily.\n\n\n\nMust feel premium.\n\n\n\nHeadings:\n\nVery large\n\ncinematic\n\nconfident\n\n\n\nUse spacing intentionally.\n\n\n\nFeels like Apple keynote.\n\n\n\nHierarchy:\n\n\n\nHero:\n\n72\342\200\22396px desktop\n\n\n\nSection headings:\n\n48\342\200\22364px\n\n\n\nBody:\n\n18\342\200\22322px\n\n\n\nReadable.\n\n\n\nMinimal clutter.\n\n\n\n---------------------------------------------------\n\nPORTFOLIO IDENTITY\n\n---------------------------------------------------\n\n\n\nName:\n\nAdarsh Singh\n\n\n\nPrimary headline:\n\n\n\n\342\200\234Building Intelligent Systems for the Future\342\200\235\n\n\n\nProfessional Positioning:\n\n\n\nAI + Data Engineer building scalable intelligent systems.\n\n\n\nCore domains:\n\n\n\n- Data Engineering\n\n- Generative AI\n\n- RAG\n\n- LLMs\n\n- Cloud\n\n- Distributed Systems\n\n- ETL\n\n- Backend Engineering\n\n\n\nCurrent Experience:\n\nCapgemini\n\nAI & Data Engineering\n\n\n\nLocation:\n\nBengaluru, India\n\n\n\nGitHub:\n\nhttps://github.com/Adarsh-Singh07\n\n\n\nLinkedIn:\n\nhttps://linkedin.com/in/adarshsingh45\n\n\n\nEmail:\n\nadarsh2001gop@gmail.com\n\n\n\n---------------------------------------------------\n\nSIGNATURE FEATURE\n\n---------------------------------------------------\n\n\n\nMULTI ROLE PROFILE TOGGLE\n\n\n\nThis is one of the most important features.\n\n\n\nImplement:\n\n\n\nGeneral \342\206\224 Data Engineer\n\n\n\nArchitecture MUST be scalable.\n\n\n\nLater we will add:\n\n\n\n- AI Engineer\n\n- ML Engineer\n\n- Backend Engineer\n\n\n\nWhen toggle changes:\n\n\n\nEntire content morphs dynamically.\n\n\n\nExample:\n\n\n\nGENERAL:\n\nShows everything.\n\n\n\nDATA ENGINEER:\n\nReorders portfolio.\n\n\n\nChanges:\n\n\n\n- hero subtitle\n\n- projects priority\n\n- skills priority\n\n- certifications priority\n\n- timeline emphasis\n\n- blog recommendations\n\n\n\nNo page reload.\n\n\n\nSmooth morph animation.\n\n\n\nUse mock JSON configuration system:\n\n\n\n/data/profileModes.ts\n\n\n\nExample:\n\n\n\ngeneralProfile\n\ndataEngineerProfile\n\n\n\nEasy to scale later.\n\n\n\n---------------------------------------------------\n\nWEBSITE STRUCTURE\n\n---------------------------------------------------\n\n\n\nBuild complete frontend with these 5 sections/pages.\n\n\n\n---------------------------------------------------\n\nSTEP 1 \342\200\224 HOMEPAGE HERO\n\n---------------------------------------------------\n\n\n\nGoal:\n\n\n\nInstant luxury first impression.\n\n\n\nMust feel:\n\n\n\n\342\200\234Damn, this person is premium.\342\200\235\n\n\n\nSECTION:\n\n\n\nLuxury floating navbar.\n\n\n\nNavbar:\n\n\n\nLeft:\n\nAS monogram logo\n\n\n\nCenter:\n\nAbout\n\nProjects\n\nSkills\n\nCertifications\n\nBlogs\n\nJourney\n\nContact\n\n\n\nRight:\n\nGeneral \342\206\224 Data Engineer toggle\n\nTheme switch\n\nResume button\n\n\n\nNavbar behavior:\n\n\n\nInitially transparent.\n\n\n\nOn scroll:\n\n\n\nTransforms into luxury glass navbar.\n\n\n\nSubtle blur.\n\n\n\nPremium animation.\n\n\n\n---------------------------------------------------\n\n\n\nHero section:\n\n\n\nSplit layout.\n\n\n\nLEFT:\n\n\n\nPremium badge:\n\nAI + DATA ENGINEER\n\n\n\nMassive headline:\n\n\n\n\342\200\234Building\n\nIntelligent Systems\n\nfor the Future\342\200\235\n\n\n\nSubtext:\n\nAI + Data Engineer crafting scalable systems using GenAI, RAG, ETL, Cloud and intelligent automation.\n\n\n\nButtons:\n\n\n\n1. Explore Projects\n\n2. View Resume\n\n\n\nTrust row:\n\n\n\nCapgemini\n\nAzure\n\nAWS\n\nGCP\n\nRAG\n\nLLMs\n\n\n\nRIGHT:\n\n\n\nPremium abstract avatar.\n\n\n\nNOT personal image yet.\n\n\n\nUse:\n\n\n\nLuxury orb composition.\n\n\n\nRequirements:\n\n\n\n- floating orb\n\n- glass rings\n\n- ambient glow\n\n- elegant futuristic visual\n\n- cinematic depth\n\n\n\nNo cyberpunk.\n\n\n\nFeels luxury.\n\n\n\n---------------------------------------------------\n\nSTEP 2 \342\200\224 BENTO + FEATURED PROJECTS\n\n---------------------------------------------------\n\n\n\nPremium asymmetrical bento layout.\n\n\n\nCards:\n\n\n\n1. FEATURED PROJECT\n\nAgentic AI + RAG Platform\n\n\n\nInclude:\n\nDocker\n\nREST APIs\n\nWebSockets\n\nRAG\n\nAgentic AI\n\nMicroservices\n\n\n\nMetrics:\n\n18% projected uplift\n\n60% faster support\n\n\n\nCTA:\n\nView Case Study\n\n\n\n---------------------------------------------------\n\n\n\n2. CORE EXPERTISE\n\n\n\nDisplay:\n\n\n\nData Engineering\n\nGenAI\n\nRAG\n\nLLMs\n\nCloud\n\nDistributed Systems\n\n\n\n---------------------------------------------------\n\n\n\n3. CERTIFICATIONS\n\n\n\nLuxury stacked cards:\n\n\n\nAI-102\n\nAWS AI Practitioner\n\nGoogle GenAI Leader\n\nAZ-900\n\nAI-900\n\n\n\n---------------------------------------------------\n\n\n\n4. EXPERIENCE\n\n\n\nCapgemini\n\n\n\nAnalyst \342\200\223 AI & Data Engineering\n\n\n\n---------------------------------------------------\n\n\n\nBelow:\n\n\n\nFEATURED ENGINEERING WORK\n\n\n\nProjects:\n\n\n\n1. Agentic AI + RAG Platform\n\n(Hero Project)\n\n\n\n2. Indian Sign Language ML Translation\n\n\n\n3. Email Campaign Automation with OpenAI\n\n\n\nPremium project cards.\n\n\n\nNo GitHub portfolio style.\n\n\n\nFeels like product showcase.\n\n\n\n---------------------------------------------------\n\nSTEP 3 \342\200\224 SKILLS + CERTIFICATIONS\n\n---------------------------------------------------\n\n\n\nHeading:\n\n\n\nEngineering Capability\n\n\n\nSubheading:\n\nBuilding scalable systems across Data, AI, Cloud and intelligent automation.\n\n\n\nCreate premium capability cards.\n\n\n\nCategories:\n\n\n\n1. Data Engineering\n\n\n\nETL\n\nSQL\n\nDatabricks\n\nTransformation\n\nDistributed Processing\n\n\n\n2. Generative AI\n\n\n\nLLMs\n\nRAG\n\nAgentic AI\n\nTransformers\n\nNLP\n\nPyTorch\n\nTensorFlow\n\n\n\n3. Cloud\n\n\n\nAzure\n\nGCP\n\nBigQuery\n\nVertex AI\n\nDocker\n\nREST APIs\n\n\n\n4. Backend\n\n\n\nPython\n\nMicroservices\n\nCI/CD\n\nDistributed Systems\n\nGit\n\n\n\n5. Visualization\n\n\n\nPower BI\n\nTableau\n\nLooker\n\nMatplotlib\n\n\n\nNO progress bars.\n\n\n\nNO percentage circles.\n\n\n\nLuxury cards only.\n\n\n\n---------------------------------------------------\n\n\n\nCertifications Wall:\n\n\n\nFeatured:\n\n\n\n- AI-102\n\n- AWS AI Practitioner\n\n- Google GenAI Leader\n\n- Professional Cloud Developer\n\n- AZ-900\n\n- AI-900\n\n\n\nCards feel:\n\n\n\nverified\n\npremium\n\nenterprise-grade\n\n\n\n---------------------------------------------------\n\nSTEP 4 \342\200\224 TIMELINE + BLOGS + STORY\n\n---------------------------------------------------\n\n\n\nHeading:\n\n\n\nThe Journey\n\n\n\nSubheading:\n\n\n\nFrom curiosity to building intelligent systems at scale.\n\n\n\nTimeline:\n\n\n\nCinematic horizontal storytelling.\n\n\n\nMilestones:\n\n\n\n1.