TANT)\n\n---------------------------------------------------\n\n\n\nMotion style:\n\n\n\nApple keynote \303\227 luxury automotive UI.\n\n\n\nSmooth.\n\n\n\nElegant.\n\n\n\nConfident.\n\n\n\nSubtle.\n\n\n\nNever flashy.\n\n\n\nNever gimmicky.\n\n\n\n---------------------------------------------------\n\n\n\n1. PAGE LOAD\n\n\n\nLuxury stagger reveal.\n\n\n\nBackground fade.\n\n\n\nHero reveal.\n\n\n\nNavbar reveal.\n\n\n\nOrb materializes.\n\n\n\nTiming:\n\n0.8\342\200\2231.2 sec\n\n\n\n---------------------------------------------------\n\n\n\n2. HERO ORB\n\n\n\nFloating animation:\n\n\n\ntranslateY(-10px \342\206\224 +10px)\n\n\n\nVery slow.\n\n\n\nLuxury breathing feel.\n\n\n\nAmbient glow pulse.\n\n\n\n---------------------------------------------------\n\n\n\n3. NAVBAR\n\n\n\nGlass morph on scroll.\n\n\n\nTransparent \342\206\222 premium blur.\n\n\n\nHeight subtly changes.\n\n\n\n---------------------------------------------------\n\n\n\n4. SECTION REVEAL\n\n\n\nAll sections:\n\n\n\nopacity 0 \342\206\222 1\n\ny: 40 \342\206\222 0\n\n\n\nElegant easing only.\n\n\n\n---------------------------------------------------\n\n\n\n5. HOVER STATES\n\n\n\nCards:\n\n\n\ntranslateY(-8px)\n\nscale(1.02)\n\n\n\nGlow intensifies.\n\n\n\nLuxury only.\n\n\n\n---------------------------------------------------\n\n\n\n6. ROLE TOGGLE\n\n\n\nSmooth morph animation.\n\n\n\nContent transitions.\n\n\n\nNo abrupt changes.\n\n\n\n---------------------------------------------------\n\n\n\n7. TIMELINE\n\n\n\nLine draws itself on scroll.\n\n\n\nMilestones stagger reveal.\n\n\n\n---------------------------------------------------\n\n\n\n8. BUTTONS\n\n\n\nMicro interactions.\n\n\n\nSoft magnetic hover.\n\n\n\nSubtle glow.\n\n\n\n---------------------------------------------------\n\nRESPONSIVENESS\n\n---------------------------------------------------\n\n\n\nFully responsive.\n\n\n\nDesktop-first.\n\n\n\nPerfect mobile experience.\n\n\n\nNo broken spacing.\n\n\n\nLuxury preserved on all devices.\n\n\n\n---------------------------------------------------\n\nCODE QUALITY\n\n---------------------------------------------------\n\n\n\nUse:\n\n\n\nclean architecture\n\nmodular components\n\nreusable UI system\n\nclean folder structure\n\nstrict TypeScript\n\nbest practices\n\n\n\nCreate:\n\n\n\ncomponents/\n\nsections/\n\nanimations/\n\nhooks/\n\nservices/\n\ndata/\n\nconstants/\n\ntypes/\n\n\n\nKeep backend-ready.\n\n\n\nUse mock JSON now.\n\n\n\n---------------------------------------------------\n\nFINAL GOAL\n\n---------------------------------------------------\n\n\n\nThe final website should make recruiters and visitors think:\n\n\n\n\342\200\234This person is elite.\342\200\235\n\n\n\nIt must feel:\n\n\n\nluxury\n\nmemorable\n\ntrustworthy\n\nfuturistic\n\npowerful\n\npremium\n\n\n\nwithout looking over-designed.\n\n\n\nDesign ONLY the FRONTEND for now.\n\nFUTURE SCALABILITY REQUIREMENTS\n\n\n\nThe portfolio MUST be future-proof.\n\n\n\nIt should support:\n\n\n\n1. GitHub auto-sync later\n\n- repository fetching\n\n- stars\n\n- latest projects\n\n- languages\n\n- repo metadata\n\n\n\n2. Live deployed demos\n\nEach project card must support:\n\n- github URL\n\n- live demo URL\n\n- deployment status\n\n\n\n3. Dynamic role system\n\nEasy addition of:\n\n- AI Engineer\n\n- ML Engineer\n\n- Backend Engineer\n\n\n\nwithout redesign.\n\n\n\n4. CMS-ready architecture\n\nAllow future integration with:\n\n- Notion\n\n- Markdown\n\n- Headless CMS\n\n- Python backend\n\n\n\n5. Backend-ready structure\n\nCompatible with:\n\nFastAPI\n\nDjango\n\nFlask\n\n\n\nUse clean service layer.\n\n\n\nMock JSON for now.\n\n\n\nAvoid hardcoded UI logic.\n\n\n\nEverything should be data-driven.\n\n\n\nThe frontend must be production-grade and scalable for years.\n\n\n"
