    user_response: "Apply the \"Luxury / Prestige\" design theme to the app.\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_START]\nDesign name: Luxury / Prestige\nDesign instructions: Extract ONLY the styling (colors, fonts, spacing, borders, shadows, backgrounds, gradients) and layout patterns (flexbox/grid structure, component arrangement) from the Design HTML below. Do NOT replace or restructure the existing app\'s HTML elements \342\200\224 preserve all existing components, content, and functionality. Only modify CSS/styling and adjust layout containers as needed to match the theme\'s aesthetic.\nDesign HTML:                   <!doctype html>\\n                  <html style=\\\"height: 100%; margin: 0;\\\">\\n                    <head>\\n                      <meta charset=\\\"UTF-8\\\" />\\n                      <meta name=\\\"viewport\\\" content=\\\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\\\" />\\n                      <script src=\\\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tailwindcss/browser@4\\\"></script>\\n                      <link href=\\\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:opsz,wght,FILL,GRAD@20..48,100..700,0..1,-50..200\\\" rel=\\\"stylesheet\\\" />\\n                      <style>\\n                        body { margin: 0; height: 100%; display: flex; flex-direction: column; overflow: hidden; }\\n                        /* Fallback classes in case Tailwind fails to load in sandbox */\\n                        .h-full { height: 100%; }\\n                        .w-full { width: 100%; }\\n                        .flex { display: flex; }\\n                        .flex-col { flex-direction: column; }\\n                        .flex-1 { flex: 1 1 0%; }\\n                      </style>\\n                    </head>\\n                    <body>\\n                      <div class=\\\"w-[1024px] h-[768px] bg-[#050505] text-[#F5F5F7] font-sans selection:bg-[#007AFF] selection:text-white flex flex-col overflow-hidden\\\">\\n  <!-- LUXURY FLOATING NAV -->\\n  <nav class=\\\"fixed top-6 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-[90%] h-14 bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-xl border border-white/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-between px-8 z-50\\\">\\n    <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-2\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"w-8 h-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-gray-500 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-black text-sm tracking-tighter italic\\\">AS</div>\\n      <span class=\\\"text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase ml-2 opacity-80\\\">Adarsh Singh</span>\\n    </div>\\n    <div class=\\\"hidden lg:flex items-center gap-8\\\">\\n      <a href=\\\"#\\\" class=\\\"text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] font-medium opacity-60 hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity\\\">Projects</a>\\n      <a href=\\\"#\\\" class=\\\"text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] font-medium opacity-60 hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity\\\">Skills</a>\\n      <a href=\\\"#\\\" class=\\\"text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] font-medium opacity-60 hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity\\\">Journey</a>\\n      <a href=\\\"#\\\" class=\\\"text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] font-medium opacity-60 hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity\\\">Notes</a>\\n    </div>\\n    <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-4\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"flex bg-black/40 p-1 rounded-full border border-white/5\\\">\\n        <button class=\\\"px-4 py-1.5 text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider rounded-full transition-all text-white/40\\\">General</button>\\n        <button class=\\\"px-4 py-1.5 text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider rounded-full transition-all bg-white text-black\\\">Data Engineer</button>\\n      </div>\\n      <div class=\\\"w-px h-4 bg-white/10 mx-1\\\"></div>\\n      <button class=\\\"w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full hover:bg-white/10\\\">\\n        <svg class=\\\"w-4 h-4 opacity-70\\\" fill=\\\"none\\\" stroke=\\\"currentColor\\\" viewBox=\\\"0 0 24 24\\\"><path stroke-linecap=\\\"round\\\" stroke-linejoin=\\\"round\\\" stroke-width=\\\"2\\\" d=\\\"M20.354 15.354A9 9 0 018.646 3.646 9.003 9.003 0 0012 21a9.003 9.003 0 008.354-5.646z\\\"></path></svg>\\n      </button>\\n    </div>\\n  </nav>\\n\\n  <!-- MAIN CONTENT SPLIT -->\\n  <main class=\\\"flex-1 flex pt-32 px-12\\\">\\n    <!-- LEFT: HERO CONTENT -->\\n    <div class=\\\"w-[55%] flex flex-col justify-center pr-12\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 bg-[#007AFF15] border border-[#007AFF30] rounded-full mb-8\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#007AFF] animate-pulse\\\"></div>\\n        <span class=\\\"text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-[#007AFF]\\\">AI + DATA ENGINEER</span>\\n      </div>\\n      \\n      <h1 class=\\\"text-[68px] leading-[0.9] font-semibold tracking-tight text-white mb-8\\\">\\n        Building <br/>\\n        <span class=\\\"text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-white via-white to-white/30 italic font-serif\\\">Intelligent Systems</span> <br/>\\n        for the Future\\n      </h1>\\n\\n      <p class=\\\"text-lg text-white/50 leading-relaxed max-w-md mb-10\\\">\\n        Architecting scalable data ecosystems with GenAI, RAG, and distributed cloud infrastructure at Capgemini.\\n      </p>\\n\\n      <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-6\\\">\\n        <button class=\\\"px-10 py-5 bg-white text-black font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest rounded-full shadow-[0_0_40px_rgba(255,255,255,0.1)] hover:scale-105 transition-transform\\\">Explore Work</button>\\n        <button class=\\\"px-10 py-5 border border-white/20 text-white font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest rounded-full hover:bg-white/5 transition-colors\\\">Resume</button>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <div class=\\\"mt-16 flex flex-col gap-4\\\">\\n        <span class=\\\"text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] opacity-30\\\">Elite Credentials</span>\\n        <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-8 opacity-60 grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transition-all\\\">\\n          <span class=\\\"font-serif italic text-lg\\\">Capgemini</span>\\n          <div class=\\\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-white/20\\\"></div>\\n          <span class=\\\"font-sans font-bold tracking-tighter\\\">Azure AI-102</span>\\n          <div class=\\\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-white/20\\\"></div>\\n          <span class=\\\"font-sans font-bold tracking-tighter uppercase\\\">AWS Cloud</span>\\n          <div class=\\\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-white/20\\\"></div>\\n          <span class=\\\"font-serif italic text-lg\\\">Google GenAI</span>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n\\n    <!-- RIGHT: LUXURY VISUAL + MINI BENTO -->\\n    <div class=\\\"w-[45%] flex flex-col gap-6\\\">\\n      <!-- FEATURED PROJECT CARD -->\\n      <div class=\\\"relative flex-1 bg-gradient-to-br from-white/10 to-transparent border border-white/10 rounded-[40px] p-8 overflow-hidden flex flex-col\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"absolute -top-20 -right-20 w-80 h-80 bg-[#007AFF30] blur-[100px] rounded-full\\\"></div>\\n        \\n        <!-- THE LUXURY ORB -->\\n        <div class=\\\"relative flex-1 flex items-center justify-center py-4\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"relative w-48 h-48\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-tr from-[#007AFF] to-[#5AC8FA] rounded-full blur-2xl opacity-20 animate-pulse\\\"></div>\\n            <div class=\\\"absolute inset-4 border border-white/20 rounded-full rotate-45\\\"></div>\\n            <div class=\\\"absolute inset-8 border border-white/10 rounded-full -rotate-12\\\"></div>\\n            <div class=\\\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-white/30 to-black/80 rounded-full border border-white/30 shadow-inner flex items-center justify-center\\\">\\n              <div class=\\\"w-12 h-12 bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-md rounded-full border border-white/20\\\"></div>\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n\\n        <div class=\\\"mt-auto\\\">\\n          <span class=\\\"text-[10px] font-bold text-[#007AFF] uppercase tracking-widest mb-2 block\\\">Featured Case Study</span>\\n          <h3 class=\\\"text-2xl font-semibold mb-2\\\">Agentic RAG Platform</h3>\\n          <p class=\\\"text-sm text-white/40 mb-4\\\">Intelligent automation yielding 60% faster support cycles through LLM orchestration.</p>\\n          <div class=\\\"flex gap-2\\\">\\n            <span class=\\\"text-[9px] px-2 py-1 bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded text-white/60\\\">Python</span>\\n            <span class=\\\"text-[9px] px-2 py-1 bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded text-white/60\\\">OpenAI</span>\\n            <span class=\\\"text-[9px] px-2 py-1 bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded text-white/60\\\">Azure</span>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <!-- MINI METRICS GRID -->\\n      <div class=\\\"h-44 grid grid-cols-2 gap-6\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"bg-[#151515] border border-white/5 rounded-[32px] p-6 flex flex-col justify-between\\\">\\n          <span class=\\\"text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest opacity-40 italic\\\">Efficiency</span>\\n          <div>\\n            <div class=\\\"text-3xl font-serif italic\\\">+18%</div>\\n            <div class=\\\"text-[10px] uppercase opacity-40\\\">Projected Uplift</div>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n        <div class=\\\"bg-[#151515] border border-white/5 rounded-[32px] p-6 flex flex-col justify-between\\\">\\n          <span class=\\\"text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest opacity-40 italic\\\">Experience</span>\\n          <div>\\n            <div class=\\\"text-3xl font-serif italic\\\">Capgemini</div>\\n            <div class=\\\"text-[10px] uppercase opacity-40\\\">Analyst Engineering</div>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n  </main>\\n\\n  <!-- FOOTER RAIL -->\\n  <footer class=\\\"h-20 border-t border-white/5 px-12 flex items-center justify-between\\\">\\n    <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-12\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"flex flex-col\\\">\\n        <span class=\\\"text-[9px] uppercase tracking-widest opacity-30\\\">Current Location</span>\\n        <span class=\\\"text-[11px] font-medium\\\">Bengaluru, India</span>\\n      </div>\\n      <div class=\\\"flex flex-col\\\">\\n        <span class=\\\"text-[9px] uppercase tracking-widest opacity-30\\\">Specialization</span>\\n        <span class=\\\"text-[11px] font-medium\\\">AI & Data Ecosystems</span>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n    <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-8 text-[11px] font-semibold opacity-40\\\">\\n      <a href=\\\"#\\\" class=\\\"hover:text-white transition-colors\\\">LinkedIn</a>\\n      <a href=\\\"#\\\" class=\\\"hover:text-white transition-colors\\\">GitHub</a>\\n      <a href=\\\"#\\\" class=\\\"hover:text-white transition-colors\\\">Twitter</a>\\n      <div class=\\\"w-px h-3 bg-white/20\\\"></div>\\n      <span class=\\\"italic font-serif\\\">\302\251 2026 Adarsh Singh</span>\\n    </div>\\n  </footer>\\n</div>\\n                    </body>\\n                  </html>\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_END]"
